dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Buffalo County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Buffalo_Roads_2018.gdb.[Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways or carriageways in a local government. Typically, this information is compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. It also serves as a source for public works and other agencies that are responsible for the active management of the road network.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[Road Centerlines]
